am al-Tirmidhi commented, \u201cThe scholars differed over the night prayer in\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14061,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/08\/who-is-a-martyr\/","url_meta":{"origin":34159,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Martyrs: Who do you consider your martyrs?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 8, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWho do you consider a martyr among you?\u201d They said, \u201cThe one who is killed in the way of Allah.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cIf that were so, there are few martyrs in my nation.\u201d They said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39918,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/23\/let-them-work\/","url_meta":{"origin":34159,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Forgiveness: Let them not take Allah\u2019s mercy for granted","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 23, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever meets Allah without associating any partners with Him, performs the five prayers, and fasts the month of Ramadan, then he will be forgiven.\u201d I said, \u201cShall I not give them glad tidings, O Messenger\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_c